WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Let's count ocean waves together!

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Waves come in regular patterns that we can predict and count.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Small waves, big waves - each one tells us about the ocean.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Counting waves helps scientists understand ocean conditions.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Mathematics and marine science work hand in hand!